These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, swisher, ritmeester, bolivar
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is between the swisher-smoker and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Cigar      | bolivar | siglo | ritmeester   | swisher |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, ebony, emerald, lilac
There are 4 different nationalities: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. the turkish is between the person who likes emerald and the colombian##2
2. the person who likes lilac is on the far right##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the british##1
4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Color         | ebony | amber | emerald | lilac |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
House: palace, modern, tower, cottage
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, colombian, french
1. the colombian is on the right of the cottage house##1
2. the colombian is between the british and the modern house##2
3. the british is on the far left##1
4. the french is on the left of the tower house##1
5. the modern house is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| House          | cottage    | palace | modern   | tower  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony, rat
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, davidoff, fonseca, aristoff
1. the davidoff-smoker is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the old-henry-smoker and the owner of the rat##2
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Cigar   | fonseca | aristoff | old-henry | davidoff |

