.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, ice-hockey, biathlon, sailing
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Sport   | swimming        | biathlon | sailing  | ice-hockey |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving | card-games    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
There 4 different types of food: orange, spinach, apple, cherry
1. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
2. the fan of salsa is the person eating apple##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the person eating orange##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| Food         | orange | cherry | spinach   | apple |

