.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, house, punk
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, paramedic, firefighter, coach
1. the fan of gospel is the engineer##1
2. the firefighter is on the left of the engineer##1
3. the coach is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the paramedic is on the left of the coach##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the engineer and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel | electronic | house      |
| Job     | firefighter | engineer    | paramedic  | coach |

