.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bluemaster, bongani, baccarat
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, ship, van
1. the bongani-smoker is between the person driving the boat and the siglo-smoker##2
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Cigar         | bluemaster | bongani | siglo | baccarat |
| Transport   | boat         | van       | scooter    | ship         |

