.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, indie, r&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the fan of indie##1
3. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the fan of jazz and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Music-Genre    | r&b   | indie      | jazz   | house  |
| Sport   | tennis | ice-hockey | swimming | baseball |

