.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, singing, writing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, october, july, april
1. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing | writing | filmmaking |
| Birthday   | july          | october     | april  | march     |

