.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, frog, snake, turtle
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, documentary, sports
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the turtle is between the person watching sports movies and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | turtle | frog | snake     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | documentary    | sports   | adventure |

