3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Hobby         | baking      | singing | hiking  | magic-tricks |
| House   | gothic-revival | townhouse  | art-deco | cottage    |

