.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, blood-red, apricot, black
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person who likes black is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who likes yellow and the person who likes apricot##2
5. the person who likes apricot is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | black   | yellow   | blood-red | apricot |
| Sport         | baseball | basketball | rowing     | golf    |

