.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, dancer, journalist, accountant
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the librarian is between the owner of the cat and the accountant##2
3. the accountant is on the left of the librarian##1
4. the dancer is on the far right##1
5. the dancer is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Job   | journalist    | accountant     | librarian | dancer |
| Pet     | chinchilla | guinea-pig | goat       | cat     |

 